Increase Hit Points (HP) by 5 (L24)<br>
<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Classes: Dru (L34), Shm (L24)<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Skill: Alteration<br>
Allowable Targets: All<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Range to Target: 100 feet<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Resistance Check: None<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Mana Required: 100<br>
Spell Duration: Unknown<br>
Duration Formula: 10<br>
Casting Time: 6.0 seconds<br>
Spell Recovery: 2.50 seconds<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Spell cast on you: You begin to regenerate.<br>
Spell cast on someone: Soandso begins to regenerate.<br>
Spell fades: You have stopped regenerating.<br>
