<br>
The 5th-6th boss drops appear to be a bit randomised as we got that mask off 5th recently too and 6th dropped stuff we have had off 5th. The FT items are really liked by our casters.<br>
<br>
The script spontaneously bombs out occasionally even if you have several people in the ring.<br>
<br>
As to the BP, irrespective of the fact that it lacks fungal regrowth, it's a very nice BP for rogues that takes multiple groups several hours of boring slogging and appears to have about a 1 in 7 drop rate.<br>
